// $Id$

CCK widget for textfields that validates swedish zipcodes. 

* Assumes you have one field for swedish zipcode and one field for city. When enabled the city field will be disabled by javascript.
* If a valid zipcode is entered it prepopulates the city field by Javascript. When submitting the form the value is also validated. 

If the API cannot be reached the validation is disabled.

This module currently builds on the API postnummersok.se provides.

INSTALLATION

1. Enable the module
2. Create a textfield for city on the content type you wish to use
3. Create a textfield for zipcode, choose swedish zipcode as widget
4. Create a node of the content type you added the fields to, enter a swedish zipcode in the field and watch how it prepopulates the city field
